clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d654ff87b1385f7f2c1887ca4f44f1c8f85a0488","tid":684633,"uid":52406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:08:38.000Z","msg":"你可以唔鍾意佢，但係無得唔尊敬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢點我自己都成日講，唔止係講緊james, 仲有好多其他球員，包括自己唔鍾意嗰d"},{"pid":"d140e6276eb0901fb8d51bee852fcabcfc15315d","tid":684633,"uid":55545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:11:41.000Z","msg":"毫無疑問 占士真係幫騎士幫到搏埋條老命 佢已經唔後生<br />\n<br />\n騎士今年啲人真係 打出對唔住自己身價既波<br />\n<br />\n有人唔鍾意占士係又話唔係又話 <br />\n<br />\n但唔可否認佢既能力 我唔敢話佢係最偉大 <br />\n<br />\n但佢真係其中一個我真心佩服佢既球星 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45e7311ead3a11476c619928749bfd19ba2ad46","tid":684633,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"MJ唔退休可以8連冠 lbj點都比唔上"},{"pid":"93b41d0e5b8bb3b142cf303bc3743b1a3c330209","tid":684633,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"好撚煩啊 fuck off la James"},{"pid":"c810588f28279ec69cd08d2a65b1c147692994c8","tid":684633,"uid":158494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45e7311ead3a11476c619928749bfd19ba2ad46","tid":684633,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:14:27.000Z","msg":"MJ唔退休可以8連冠 lbj點都比唔上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:37:01.000Z","msg":"咁佢係退左休呀嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}